A warm Studio Ghibli-style illustration of a father and young twin boys sitting together on a cozy bedroom floor at twilight, soft golden lamplight casting gentle shadows. The father gestures thoughtfully while the curious boys listen intently, their faces showing wonder and contemplation. Around them, three softly glowing orbs float in the air—one warm amber near the head, one rose-pink near the chest, one deeper red lower—symbolizing different emotions without being explicit. Through a window behind them, stars are beginning to appear in a dusky purple-orange sky. The scene radiates tenderness, curiosity, and the intimate magic of parent-child conversations. Soft watercolor textures, gentle linework, dreamy atmosphere with muted earth tones and warm highlights.
